By induction on n, with the base cases following from Lemma  and Corollary  respectively. In the inductive step, we need to show that for all f,g\colon  \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
